---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Narrow March — Follow the Lamb into the Fire">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero-banner.jpg" alt="A knight stands before a burning city, bearing the cross" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">The Narrow March</h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">"Do not follow the Lamb for comfort.<br />Follow Him into the fire."</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/daily-crusader" class="btn btn-primary">Start the Daily Crusader</a>
        <a href="/newsletter" class="btn btn-outline btn-outline-light">Join the Newsletter</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission">
        <h2 class="section-title">The War Has Never Ended</h2>
        <p class="mission-text">
          The Narrow March exists for men who understand that faith is not passive. It is active, costly, and daily.
          The crusade is internal before it is external. The enemy is not flesh and blood but principalities — and the battlefield is the heart.
        </p>
        <p class="mission-text">
          We are not building an audience. We are forging soldiers — armored in prayer, marching through cities of sin like salt through decay.
          Not soldiers of empire, but of eternity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Two Newsletter Cards -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="newsletter-grid">
        <div class="card newsletter-card">
          <h3 class="card-title">The Daily Crusader</h3>
          <p class="card-subtitle">365 Days of Warrior Faith</p>
          <p class="card-desc">
            A devotional in your inbox every morning at 5 AM. Short, direct, rooted in Scripture — built to sharpen your discipline and anchor your day before the world gets a word in.
          </p>
          <a href="https://crusader.thenarrowmarch.com" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card newsletter-card">
          <h3 class="card-title">The Narrow March</h3>
          <p class="card-subtitle">Daily Exegesis</p>
          <p class="card-desc">
            Every week, one passage. Every day, we go deeper. Daily exegesis tied to the week's sermon — so the Word isn't something you heard once. It's something you carry.
          </p>
          <a href="https://blog.thenarrowmarch.com" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Verse Banner -->
  <section class="verse-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote class="verse">
        <p>"Enter through the narrow gate. For wide is the gate and broad is the road that leads to destruction, and many enter through it. But small is the gate and narrow the road that leads to life, and only a few find it."</p>
        <cite>— Matthew 7:13-14</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sermons Teaser -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Sermons</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Verse-by-verse exposition through the books of the Bible.</p>
      <a href="/sermons" class="btn btn-outline">Coming Soon</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Hero ===== */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .hero-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--hero-overlay);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: #fff;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-outline-light {
    color: #fff;
    border-color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-outline-light:hover {
    background: #fff;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  /* ===== Mission ===== */
  .mission {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .mission-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  /* ===== Newsletter Grid ===== */
  .newsletter-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .newsletter-card {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .card-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ===== Verse Banner ===== */
  .verse-banner {
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .verse {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .verse p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .verse cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .newsletter-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
